"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-othersport-1931343-Olympics-2024-Tamara-Potocka-collapsed-Slovakia\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  The Slovakian Olympic team have confirmed their swimmer Tamara Potocka has \\\"communicated\\\" with doctors after collapsing at theParis 2024 Gameson Friday.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 154, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 58, \"end\": 64, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tamar_of_Georgia\", \"score\": 0.6907608566859789, \"rank\": 0.4124052621669345, \"text\": \"Tamara\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tamar_of_Georgia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tamar_of_Georgia\"}, {\"begin\": 65, \"end\": 72, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potocki_family\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Potocka\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potocki_family\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potocki_family\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Potocka collapsed to the ground on the pool deck immediately after the women's 200-metre medley as medics rushed to her aid.She was taken away on a stretcherand was spotted with an oxygen mask fitted to her face.\", \"from\": 156, \"to\": 368, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It has now been confirmed by Slovakia's Olympic team that the 21-year-old suffered an asthma attack and she has been given oxygen therapy treatment.\", \"from\": 370, \"to\": 518, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Potocka is understood to be conscious and was able to communicate with doctors when undertaking the treatment.\", \"from\": 520, \"to\": 630, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She has been taken to hospital for further medical supervision.\", \"from\": 632, \"to\": 695, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The scary incident took place after Potocka had finished seventh in the third heat of the event in the morning session at La Defense Arena in Nanterre.\", \"from\": 697, \"to\": 8